description: FINAL RELEASE - Improved Price! Last available 1 bed plus den layout on the 8th floor with corner exposure and oversized windows offering abundant natural light and direct views of the grand pool. Includes 1 garage valet parking space. Enjoy luxury resort-style living in Boston’s vibrant Seaport with over 50,000 SF of resident-only amenities, including 1 indoor and 2 outdoor pools, a state-of-the-art fitness center, indoor basketball court, hot yoga studio, and sports simulator. The Club Level features fireplace lounges, private dining, a library, and expansive terraces with grilling stations and fire pits. The 22nd floor Sky Lounge and Terrace provide stunning views of the downtown skyline, perfect for entertaining. Residents also enjoy 24/7 concierge, doorman, and porter services. Extra storage available for purchase.
